'''Jedi Guardians''', also known as a '''Warrior Masters''', were a group within the [[Jedi Order]]. The [[Processional Way]] in front of the [[Imperial Palace|Jedi Temple]] on [[Coruscant]] was terminated in a staircase that was crowned with the statues of two Jedi Warrior Masters and two [[Sage Master]]s.<ref name="CL" /> The [[Zygerrian]] [[Jedi Knight]]<ref name="GoH">''[[Star Wars: Galaxy of Heroes]]''</ref> [[Tosan]]<ref name="AoR">[[Age of Republic - Obi-Wan Kenobi 1|''Age of Republic - Obi-Wan Kenobi'' 1]]</ref> was a Jedi Guardian.<ref name="GoH" />

